          Jess has built and launched dozens of web products. The son of two teachers, he’s passionate about stretching the boundaries of education. He won’t rest until you are teaching a course on Enroll.


      .col-sm-6.about-profile.clearfix
        = image_tag 'vojto.png', height: 80
        %h5
          Vojtech Rinik
          %a{:href => "http://rinik.net/"}<
            %i.icon-home
          %a{:href => "http://github.com/vojto/"}<
            %i.icon-social-github
          %a{:href => "http://twitter.com/_vojto/"}
